      <title>阿联酋创建化工巨头的交易因奥地利选举而推迟</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/uae-deal-to-create-chemicals-giant-delayed-by-austria-elections</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于欧洲国家即将举行的选举使决策变得复杂化，阿拉伯联合酋长国和奥地利国有能源生产商计划创建一家全球化学品巨头的交易面临数月的额外延误。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/uae-deal-to-create-chemicals-giant-delayed-by-austria-elections</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 17:18:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
